    "updated_at": "2015-10-23T19:09:19Z",
    "body": "Neither Windows 7 or Linux have spellchecking built-in, you have to implement it yourself. Implementing a built-in API that only works on one platform yet feels like it should work everywhere seems...odd?\n"
  },
