    "updated_at": "2015-10-23T19:13:05Z",
    "body": "OS X users are used to having spellchecking in text boxes by default. It would be very non-native not having that. If other OSes doesn't provide it built-in, users won't expect it there either. According to [node-spellchecker](https://github.com/atom/node-spellchecker) there's a spellcheck API in Windows 8.\n"
